handleOkCommand

public void handleOkCommand(javax.microedition.lcdui.Displayable source)
Handles the Ok command. If the command is from the ChatNameScreen the chat name is set. If the command is from the PeerListScreen the peers are set.

Parameters:
source - the displayable on which the command occured

handleSendCommand

public void handleSendCommand()
Handles the Send command. Appends the chat name and prompt character to then beginning of the message. If the peerNumbers vector contains some peer numbers the doSend() method of the MessageHandler is called otherwise an alert is displayed notifying the user that no peers have been set.
